HEADWORD: Cutaway
<hw>Cut"a*way`</hw> <pr>(k⟦ucr⟧t"⟦adot⟧*w⟦amac⟧`)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<def>Having a part cut off or away; having the corners rounded or cut
